title: Will Bobby Write A Third Book? + Keith Urban Tells Lunchbox The Worst Part Of Being A Celebrity

description:
Bobby talks about the possibility of writing a third book. Lunchbox talks to Keith Urban about the worst part of being famous. Amy tries to use cool lingo with Kane Brown and fails. Also, Matt Stell stops by the studio.
